# Pursuit of Hoppyness
PursuitOfHoppyness is a useful API used to help people find the perfect beer for them which they can search through different breweries and venues as well as specifications of the different beers.  


# group Beers 

## Beer Collection [/beers]

### List All Beers [GET /api/beers]
Retrieve a list of all beers from the PursuitOfHoppyness database.

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "id": "0",
                "name": "Shiner Bock"
            },
            {
                "id": "1",
                "name": "Heineken"
            },
            {
                "id": "2",
                "name": "Blue Moon"
            }
        ]
### Specific Beer [GET /api/beers/{beer_id}]
Retrieve details of a specific beer using its ID from the database including the beer's name, brewery, labels, style, venue, and if it's organic or not.

+ Parameters
    + beer_id (number, required) - the unique id of the beer as an integer
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "abv": 5.2
                "brewery_id": 259,
                "ibu": 33
                "id": "3558",
                "labels": "https://untappd.akamaized.net/site/beer_logos/beer-3558_fe9a9_sm.jpeg",
                "name": "Brooklyn Lager",
                "rating": 3.506
                "state_id": "NY",
                "style": "Lager - Vienna"
                
            }
        ]


