# group State 

## State Collection [/state]

### List all States [GET /api/states]
Retrieves a list of all of the states and their abbreviationsixe.
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "abbreviation": "TX",
                "name": "Texas"
            },
            {
                "abbreviation": "CA",
                "name": "California"
            }
            {
                "abbreviation": "FL",
                "name": "Florida"
            }
        ]
        
### Specific States [GET /api/state/{state_abbreviation}]
Retrieves the specific details of a location using its ID from the database including its name, capital, and media.

+ Parameters
    + state_abbreviation (string, required) - the unique abbreviation of the state as a string

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "abbreviation": "TX",
                "capital": "Austin",
                "flower": "Bluebonnet",
                "media": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flag_of_Texas#/media/File:Flag_of_Texas.svg",
                "name": "Texas"
            }
        
        ]